ygData.messageBody:
Hi!

Yes Steamfront is a good place. What I usually do with all my toons is once I hit 5, got to SF and pick on the Kobolds then Mino camp off to the North of the zone entrance until about 10. Then I head over to Crushbone and get in a Throne Room Group or Wall Group until about 15/17 then I head to Paludal Caverns and go to 25 there. After that I then head to Lake Of Ill Omen and get to about 30. After that, I have no idea what to tell you.

I didn't catch what server you were on but if you're on Solusek Ro, look me up!

Later!
Durgaa - 24 - Ranger
Shizney - 21 - Mage
